    "after-sirens": {
      "id": "after-sirens",
      "text": "The path winds deeper into the Labyrinth. You pass chambers filled with wonders - a room where water flows upward, a hall of mirrors showing different possible futures, a garden of stone flowers.\n\n\"The Labyrinth is incredible,\" {{PLAYER1_NAME}} says. \"Daedalus really was a genius.\"\n\nFinally, you reach a grand doorway carved with sphinx images. Beyond it, you sense something waiting.\n\n\"This is it,\" {{PLAYER2_NAME}} says. \"The Sphinx's chamber. Are you ready?\"\n\nYou check your items - the Ariadne's thread trailing behind you, any gifts you've collected, and most importantly, everything you've learned.\n\n*Final Challenge: In Greek myths, the greatest challenges test both mind and heart!*",
      "choices": [
