    "sphinx-riddle": {
      "id": "sphinx-riddle",
      "text": "The Sphinx smiles. \"Very well. Here is my riddle:\"\n\n\"I have keys but no locks. I have space but no room. You can enter but can't go inside. What am I?\"\n\nYou think hard. Keys but no locks... space but no room... enter but can't go inside...\n\n{{PLAYER2_NAME}} starts working through it. \"Keys could mean piano keys? No locks, so not door keys...\"\n\n{{PLAYER1_NAME}} adds, \"Space but no room - like outer space? No, wait... the space bar!\"\n\n\"A keyboard!\" you say together. \"You can press enter but can't go inside it!\"\n\n*Riddle Strategy: Break riddles into parts and think about multiple meanings of each word!*",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "\"The answer is a keyboard!\"",
          "nextNodeId": "sphinx-impressed"
        }
