    "sphinx-stumped": {
      "id": "sphinx-stumped",
      "text": "The Sphinx growls in frustration. \"I cannot solve it. What IS the answer?\"\n\n\"Stress,\" you say. \"When people have less stress, they feel like they have more peace, more freedom, more happiness!\"\n\nThe Sphinx looks genuinely impressed. \"Clever, clever children! It's been centuries since anyone stumped me.\"\n\nHer demeanor shifts. \"I am bound by my word. You may ask me one question, and I must answer truthfully.\"\n\nThis is your chance to either take the owl directly or learn something useful!\n\n*Mythological Rules: Magical creatures in Greek myths always kept their promises - it was part of their nature!*",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "\"Give us Athena's owl and let us go.\"",
          "nextNodeId": "winning-ending"
