    "sphinx-impressed": {
      "id": "sphinx-impressed",
      "text": "\"A keyboard!\" the Sphinx repeats, then laughs - a sound like rumbling thunder. \"Correct! I must update my riddles - that one is too old.\"\n\nShe rises and opens the owl's cage. The owl flies to {{PLAYER1_NAME}}'s shoulder, hooting gratefully.\n\n\"You've earned this victory fairly,\" the Sphinx says. \"I honor the ancient rules. The owl is yours.\"\n\nShe looks almost pleased. \"It's been refreshing to meet mortals who use their minds. Most just try to fight me. That never ends well for them.\"\n\n\"Before you go - follow your thread back, and you'll find the exit. The Labyrinth will let you leave.\"\n\n*Victory Through Wisdom: The greatest Greek heroes won through cleverness, not just strength!*",
      "choices": [
        {
